quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  81,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  81,1,jab Sooraj lapait diya jaye ga
  81,2,aur jab tarre bikhar jayen ge
  81,3,aur jab pahar chalaye jayen ge
  81,4,aur jab das mahinay ki haamla ontniyan apne haal par chore di jayen gi
  81,5,aur jab jungli janwar samaitt kar ikathay kar diye jayen ge
  81,6,aur jab samandar bahrakna diye jayen ge
  81,7,aur jab jaanen ( jismon se ) joor di jayen gi
  81,8,aur jab zindah gaari hui larki se poocha jaye ga
  81,9,ke woh kis qasoor mein maari gayi ?
  81,10,aur jab aamaal naame khole jayen ge
  81,11,aur jab aasman ka parda hata diya jaye ga
  81,12,aur jab jahannum dehkai jaye gi
  81,13,aur jab jannat qareeb le aayi jaye gi
  81,14,uss waqt har shakhs ko maloom ho jaye ga ke woh kya le kar aaya hai
  81,15,"pas nahi, mein qasam khata hon"
  81,16,palatnay aur choup jaane walay taron ki
  81,17,aur raat ki jabkay woh rukhsat hui
  81,18,aur subah ki jabkay is ne saans liya
  81,19,yeh fi al waqea aik buzurag pegham Bar ka qoul hai
  81,20,"jo barri tawanai rakhta hai, arsh walay ke haan buland martaba hai"
  81,21,"wahan uss ka hukum maana jata hai, woh ba aetmaad hai"
  81,22,aur ( ae ahal mecca ) tumhara Rafeeq Majnoon nahi hai
  81,23,uss ne uss pegham Bar ko roshan ufaq par dekha hai
  81,24,aur woh ghaib ( ke iss ilm ko logon taq pohanchanay ) ke muamlay mein bukheel nahi hai
  81,25,aur yeh kisi shetan mardood ka qoul nahi hai
  81,26,phir tum log kidhar chalay ja rahay ho ?
  81,27,yeh to saaray Jahan walon ke liye aik nasiyaat hai
  81,28,tum mein se har uss shakhs ke liye jo raah raast par chalna chahta ho
  81,29,aur tumahray chahanay se kuch nahi hota jab taq Allah Rab alaalmin nah chahay
